  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    NIS Regulations - what non-UK digital service providers operating in the UK should do after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What organisations based outside of the UK  offering services in the UK must do to comply with the regulations covering the security of network and information systems.</p>

  </div>
</div>

